organic.title: Trade Setup for March 11: Nifty awaits key macro data ...
organic.description: The Nifty Bank snapped a six-day winning streak on Thursday but managed to end the truncated week with gains of over a percent.

organic.title: Inflation, BANK NIFTY nears all-time high, F&O cues to watch
organic.description: Last week's positive momentum in the banking sector lifted both the BANK NIFTY and the NIFTY50. All eyes will now be on this week's inflation data.
